**/.dockerignore
````````
# Git files
**/.git
**/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes

# Visual Studio files
**/.vs
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/*.user
**/*.suo
**/*.userosscache
**/*.sln.docstates

# Build results
**/bin
**/obj
**/out
**/.build

# NuGet Packages
**/packages
**/*.nupkg
**/*.snupkg

# Test Results
**/TestResults
**/*.trx

# Docker files (don't copy these into the image)
**/.dockerignore
**/docker-compose*
**/Dockerfile*

# CI/CD
**/.github
**/.gitlab-ci.yml
**/.travis.yml

# Documentation (optional - remove if you want docs in image)
**/README*.md
**/LICENSE
**/DOCKER_DEPLOYMENT.md
**/SERVER_DEPLOYMENT_GUIDE.md
**/*.md

# Scripts (optional - remove if you need these in image)
**/build-and-deploy.sh
**/build-and-deploy.ps1

# Environment files (sensitive data)
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/appsettings.Development.json

# Logs
**/logs
**/*.log

# Database files
**/*.db
**/*.sqlite
**/*.mdf
**/*.ldf

# OS files
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/desktop.ini

# Temporary files
**/tmp
**/temp
**/*.tmp
**/*.bak
**/*.swp
**/*~

# Node modules (if any frontend tooling)
**/node_modules
**/npm-debug.log
**/yarn-error.log

# Keep certain files (negation)
!**/.gitignore
!.git/HEAD
!.git/config
!.git/packed-refs
!.git/refs/heads/**
